title: John Vanderslice from Tiny Telephone Studio
itunes:title: John Vanderslice from Tiny Telephone Studio
description:
Episode 160 - I had the absolute pleasure of speaking to prolific indie rock musician and talented producer (Death Cab For Cutie, The Mountain Goats), John Vanderslice. He was very open in discussing his attitudes towards touring, drug use and how important hip-hop his in his life. It's a free flowing conversation that I think you will enjoy.
